Good morning dear <!channel>,
I hope you are doing well on this Week 15 :rocket:

• *Please don't forget to answer the survey tonight* :white_check_mark: It really helps us to have your feedback.
• *It's time for the 1 on 1s again*! It's been a long time we haven't talk. I will send you a message to set this up during the week. As always, it is just a quick conversation to know how you are feeling. Looking forward to seeing your faces :blush:
• FYI: Mariel left Ironhack and we wish her all the best. Please reach out to me from now on if you need anything.
Have a lovely day!

Your Program Manager
Joyce :sparkles:
